'''瓜達盧長腿兀鷹'''（[[学名|学名]]：''Caracara lutosa''）是一種已[[滅絕|滅絕]]的[[猛禽|猛禽]]，與[[卡拉卡拉鷹|卡拉卡拉鷹]]和[[鳳頭卡拉鷹|鳳頭卡拉鷹]]是近親。牠們最初是分類在''Polyborus''中。

在20世紀初以前，瓜達盧長腿兀鷹棲息在[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]的[[瓜達盧普島|瓜達盧普島]]。因為瓜達盧長腿兀鷹以往被認為是卡拉卡拉鷹的[[亞種|亞種]]，故後者有時會被稱為瓜達盧長腿兀鷹。牠們於2000年被定為獨立的[[物種|物種]]。<ref name=AOU2000>{{Cite journal en|author=American Ornithologists' Union (AOU)|year=2000|title=Forty-second supplement to the American Ornithologists' Union Check-list of North American Birds|journal=Auk|volume=117|issue=3|pages=847-858|doi=10.1642/0004-8038(2000)117[0847:FSSTTA]2.0.CO;2}}</ref>

早期的觀察者指瓜達盧長腿兀鷹為「惡魔」。牠們因牧羊業的獵殺及毒害而滅絕。1876年時，牠們在島內仍很普遍。<ref name="EllisNTB"/>但到了1897年時，就只見到一隻<ref name=Kaeding1905>{{Cite journal en|author=Kaeding, Henry B.|year=1905|title=Birds from the West Coast of Lower California and Adjacent Islands (Part II)|journal=Condor|volume=7|issue=4|pages=134-138|url=http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/Condor/files/issues/v007n05/p0134-p0138.pdf|access-date=2009-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081003034115/http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/Condor/files/issues/v007n05/p0134-p0138.pdf|archive-date=2008-10-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，但相信仍未消失。於1900年，Rollo Beck捕捉了9隻瓜達盧長腿兀鷹作為標本。他可能射殺了島內最後一隻卡拉卡拉鷹。<ref name=Abbott1935>{{Cite journal en|author=Abbott, C. B.|year=1933|title=Closing history of the Guadalupe Caracara|journal=Condor|volume=35|pages=10-15}}</ref>於1903年有多個未確認的報告見到牠們，但於1906年就肯定了牠們的消失。<ref name=ThayerBangs1908>{{Cite journal en|author=Thayer, John E. & Bangs, Outram|year=1908|title=The Present State of the Ornis of Guadaloupe Island|journal=Condor|volume=10|issue=3|pages=101-106|doi=10.2307/1360977|url=http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/Condor/files/issues/v010n03/p0101-p0106.pdf|access-date=2009-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205020939/http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/Condor/files/issues/v010n03/p0101-p0106.pdf|archive-date=2012-02-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

瓜達盧長腿兀鷹是其中一種[[人類|人類]]刻意滅絕的[[物種|物種]]。由於牠們有時會獵殺幼羊，牧羊業則要求殺絕牠們。<ref name="EllisNTB">{{cite book en| last = Ellis| first = Richard | title = No Turning Back: The Life and Death of Animal Species| url = https://archive.org/details/noturningbacklif00elli| publisher = Harper Perennial | date = 2004| location = New York| pages = [https://archive.org/details/noturningbacklif00elli/page/172 172]| isbn =0-06-055804-0 }}</ref>牠們的棲息地被數以萬計的[[野山羊|野山羊]]所破壞，導致了其他物種的滅絕。<ref name=Leon2003>{{Cite journal en|author=León de la Luz, José Luis; Rebman, Jon P. & Oberbauer, Thomas|year=2003|title=On the urgency of conservation on Guadalupe Island, Mexico: is it a lost paradise?|journal=Biodiversity and Conservation|volume=12|issue=5|pages=1073-1082|doi=10.1023/A:1022854211166}}</ref>

已知一種[[寄生蟲|寄生蟲]]''Acutifrons caracarensis''與瓜達盧長腿兀鷹一同滅絕。<ref name=Mey1990>{{Cite journal en|author=Mey, Eberhard |year=1990 |title=Eine neue ausgestorbene Vogel-Ischnozere von Neuseeland, ''Huiacola extinctus'' (Insecta, Phthiraptera) |journal=Zoologischer Anzeiger |volume=224 |issue=1/2 |pages=49-73 |url=http://www.phthiraptera.org/Publications/0472.pdf |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012042110/http://www.phthiraptera.org/Publications/0472.pdf |archivedate=2007-10-12 }}</ref>

目前共發現了約35個瓜達盧長腿兀鷹的標本。<ref name=Luther1996>{{Cite book en|author=Luther, Dieter|year=1996|title=Die ausgestorbenen Vögel der Welt (Die neue Brehm-Bücherei '''424''')|edition=4th ed.|language=de|publisher=Westarp-Wissenschaften, Magdeburg|location=Spektrum, Heidelberg|id=ISBN 3-89432-213-6}}</ref>這些標本分別存放在[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]、[[華盛頓|華盛頓]]及[[倫敦|倫敦]]。

